description:
It’s always good to have backup

Apply your Sunday liquid fertilizer efficiently with our custom-engineered lawn sprayers so you can get the job done in just 10 minutes. Keep a backup sprayer on hand in the event of loss or breakage, so that you won’t ever be delayed in your lawn applications.

sections.faq:
Helpful tips from yard advisors:
What’s a custom-engineered fertilizer sprayer?
It’s a hose-end sprayer head specially made for Sunday liquid fertilizer. Designed for even application and steady flow, it lets you treat your lawn in 10 minutes or less so you can get back to enjoying your yard faster.
